room_title: Escape room "DaVinci Heist" by The Escape Room USA - Columbus in Columbus
review: We had a BLAST at the Escape Room in Columbus! Willam Smith was a fabulous host and Bradley Winbush was really fun and accommodating! We stole the Mona Lisa with 2 min and 49 seconds to spare!
